title: L221-001A-CX
description: Delicate cream resham and silver katori embroidery on a tie-dye canvas in shades of rouge and flamingo form a heavenly composition. This sumptuous outfit is completed with cream pants and a beautiful silver kamdani dupatta on a lemonade pink base.

title: L221-001B-CX
description: A lovely arrangement of delicate cream resham and silver katori embroidery on a tie-dye canvas in tones of crocodile and olive green. This opulent outfit is combined with cream cambric pants and a brilliantly crafted silver kamdani dupatta on an asparagus green base.

title: L221-002A-CN
description: A stunning combination is created by this captivating style in peacock colours and delicate embroidery in resham. It is paired with dyed pants and a geometrically designed woven zari dupatta. Reign on in any occasion with this statement look.

title: L221-002B-CN
description: A striking style in multi colours and exquisite embroidery in resham form a gorgeous combination. It is teamed with dyed pants and a geometrically designed woven zari dupatta. With this statement look, you'll be able to rule any event.

title: L221-003A-CX
description: This aesthetic brings a boysenberry fantasy to life. The center panel has a full gold sequins that is embroidered with porpoise resham. This outfit is complete with boysenberry pants and an exquisite tulle dupatta to make it a must-have this season.

title: L221-003B-CX
description: This look brings life to a light taupe dream. Dull gold sequins accent the central panel, which is embroidered with porpoise resham. The design is finished off with light taupe pants and an enchanting tulle net dupatta in sage green to create a perfect look for the season.

title: L221-004A-CH
description: An incandescent Italian lace style is beautifully composed with a floral cream resham and an ikat chevron embroidered back. accompanied by matching pants and a visually stunning floral dupatta in blush pink tones.

title: L221-005A-CH
description: A stunning ivory canvas is layered with an embroidered tapestry in the dori style. Silver sequins and embellished borders provide a touch of glam. This style is paired with dyed pants and a beautiful puff patterned dupatta, which makes it perfect for the season.

title: L221-005B-CH
description: A brilliant spearmint canvas is overlaid with a dori-style embroidered brocade. Silver sequins and embroidered borders add a glittering touch. This ensemble is complete with dyed pants and a lovely puff patterned dupatta, which makes it an incredible look for the season.

title: L221-006A-CV
description: A multi-color Mughal resham with an exquisite flower pattern on a French blue base and a delicately embroidered side kali. This style comes with a pair of pants and a beautiful ethnic chnitz digitally printed dupatta in monotones of French blue. A great statement piece that will keep you looking stylish throughout the season.

title: L221-006B-CV
description: A multi-color Mughal resham with an exquisite flower pattern on a rouge-colored base and a delicately embroidered side kali. This style is completed with matching pants and a wonderful ethnic chintz dupatta that has been digitally printed in monotones of rouge. A great statement piece that will keep you looking stylish throughout the season.

title: L221-007A-CL
description: Look like a coral dream in this luminous outfit with resham craftsmanship and an ethnic flair. This ensemble is completed with matching pants and a shaded tussar silk dupatta. A stunning combination that‚Äôs going to soon become your go-to outfit for any occasion.

title: L221-007B-CL
description: In this dazzling outfit with resham craftsmanship and an ethnic flair, you'll look like a yale blue dream. This look is finished with matching pants and a shaded tussar silk dupatta. A beautiful combo that will quickly become your go-to look for every evening occasion.

title: L221-008A-CN
description: Presenting a supremely poised look in raven with a dori embroidered centre panel in off white. It is complemented with dyed pants and a lovely organza woven 3D textured dupatta to create a timeless look.

title: L221-008B-CN
description: This outfit features a highly composed navy blue appearance with a soft blue dori embroidered centre panel. It is paired with dyed pants and a wonderful organza woven 3D textured dupatta.

title: L221-009A-CH
description: A spectacular canvas with exquisite Kashmiri shawl-inspired embroidery in shades of purple and pink on a beige woven net. Completed with dyed pants and the dupatta is made of rouge-colored organza puff paste with a chinoiserie design.

title: L221-009B-CH
description: A stunning canvas with magnificent Kashmiri shawl-inspired embroidery in peacock hues on a beige woven net. Dyed pants, along with a beige-colored organza puff paste dupatta that has a chinoiserie design, complete the whole look.

title: L221-010A-CX
description: A richly detailed design featuring a stunning m√©lange of dori with pani sequins embroidery in shades of cream, ferozi, and lavender resham. It is paired with matching pants and a ferozi embroidered dupatta on organza. This outfit will quickly become your favourite in your closet.

title: L221-010B-CX
description: A deeply detailed composition with a magnificent mix of dori and pani sequins embroidered in cream, lemon, and beige resham tones. It is worn with matching pants and a yellow embroidered organza dupatta. This outfit will immediately become one of your favourites in your wardrobe.

title: L221-011A-CX
description: A French blue and baby blue hue serve as the canvas for this embroidered ensemble. A luminous combination that is paired with sky blue pants and an embroidered dupatta on tulle net. This regal look embodies everything that SS stands for; elegance with style.

title: L221-011B-CX
description: The canvas for this French-style embroidered ensemble is Laurel and Tea Green. A radiant ensemble with tea green pants and an embroidered dupatta on tulle net. This royal appearance epitomises all that SS stands for: elegance combined with flair.

title: L221-012A-CV
description: Make a statement in this meticulously crafted Kashmiri tanka ethnic design with hues of dijon, pink, and gold sequins on a black base. This alluring appearance is completed with dyed pants and a jacquard woven burnout dupatta.

title: L221-012B-CV
description: This expertly created Kashmiri tanka ethnic design with dijon and magenta sequins on a plum base surely makes a statement. The look is finished with dyed pants and a jacquard woven burnout dupatta.

title: L221-013A-CH
description: Look fabulous in this richly sequined and silver tilla-embroidered Raven outfit inspired by Balochi culture. This ensemble is finished with dyed pants and a pearl-printed black crushed organza dupatta that‚Äôll always make a striking statement.

title: L221-013B-CH
description: Look amazing in this lavishly sequined and silver tilla-embroidered ruby-red Balochi-inspired outfit. This look is complemented with dyed pants and a pearl-printed ruby red crushed organza dupatta that will always stand out.

title: L221-014A-CL
description: A dori-embroidered ensemble rendered in cadet and turquoise blue, along with an exquisite floral resham border. This look is accompanied by beige pants and a contrasting blue Kamdani dupatta to create a dreamy appearance.

title: L221-014B-CL
description: A dori-embroidered ensemble in rouge and flamingo pink, with a beautiful floral resham border. This ensemble is completed with rouge pants and a contrasting watercolour Kamdani dupatta, creating an ethereal look.

title: L221-015A-CV
description: A magnificent look with a finely embroidered pointillism shirt in cream and beige resham on a salmon base. This outfit is made up of beige pants and a beautiful dupatta in a suzani style with floral patterns. The result is an ethereal and feminine ensemble.

title: L221-015B-CV
description: A remarkable effect is achieved by a skillfully embroidered pointillism shirt in cream and beige resham on a corn flower base. This outfit is made up of beige pants and a mesmerizing dupatta made of suzani with a floral pattern. The outcome is an ethereal and feminine ensemble.

title: M221-001A-CM
description: This gorgeous ensemble epitomizes sheer perfection. It features Mughal-inspired embroidery in cream on a hot pink canvas, creating a one-of-a-kind look.

title: M221-003B-CI
description: A lavishly ornamented attire with exquisite embroidery inspired by Kashmiri shawl in lush tones of teal blue and flamingo. This look will make you seem timelessly elegant on all occasions.

title: M221-020B-CK
description: A never-before-seen combination of floral and kantha embroidery in shades of taffy pink, cream, and beige on mint green produces a gorgeous article of clothing that is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

title: M221-020A-CK
description: A never-before-seen combination of floral and kantha embroidery in shades of pink, punch, and watermelon on cream produces a gorgeous article of clothing that is sure to turn heads wherever you go.

title: M221-019B-CI
description: Style as majestic as a monarch in this mughal-inspired ensemble in charcoal, beige, and cream, creating a really one-of-a-kind look to fit your everyday needs.

title: M221-019A-CI
description: Style as majestic as a monarch in this mughal-inspired ensemble in cream, army green, and crocodile, creating a really one-of-a-kind look to fit your everyday needs.

title: M221-018B-CH
description: Elevate your style with this fabulous ensemble in punch, cerise, and fern beige on coral and expertly crafted floral cross-stitch embroidery. Putting together a one-of-a-kind style for the season.

title: M221-018A-CH
description: Elevate your style with this fabulous ensemble in punch, brick, and lavender on pale white and expertly crafted floral cross-stitch embroidery. Putting together a one-of-a-kind style for the season.

title: M221-017B-CI
description: This is a gorgeous masterpiece in cream, hot pink, bubblegum pink, and Iris, inspired by Kashmiri carpets. This breathtaking ensemble is a must-have in your wardrobe.

title: M221-017A-CI
description: This is a gorgeous masterpiece in royal blue, cobalt blue, sapphire blue, and cream inspired by Kashmiri carpets. This breathtaking ensemble is a must-have in your wardrobe.

title: M221-016B-CH
description: A dreamy ensemble in shades of soft blush pink, cream, pearl, and rose with intricate embroidery of chinoiserie. This gorgeous look is bound to make a statement wherever you go.

title: M221-016A-CH
description: A dreamy ensemble in shades of mint, cream, and pearl paste with intricate embroidery of chinoiserie. This gorgeous look is bound to make a statement wherever you go.

title: M221-015B-CI
